# TypeScript

- Use strict TypeScript; avoid `any`.
- Define shared types in `types/` `.ts` files, import into components.
- Keep component props strongly typed.

```typescript
// ❌ BAD
const data: any = await fetchData();

// ✅ GOOD — type in types/
import type { HealthCheckData } from "@/types";
```
